channel.title: Now we have whonix sourceforge key expired?
channel.description:
I'm aware of the tor expired key but today i got this first: [code]Debian Package Update Check Result: Could not check for software updates! (apt-get code: 100) Please manually check: (Open a terminal, Start menu -> Applications -> System -> Terminal.) sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get dist-upgrade[/code]
and then when i did "sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get dist-upgrade" i got this: [code] E: Release file for http://sourceforge.net/projects/whonixdevelopermetafiles/files/internal/dists/stable/Release is expired (invalid since 22h 33min 30s). Updates for this repository will not be applied.[/code]
